          <button onclick="bulkDeleteSelected()" id="bulkDeleteBtn" style="display:none; padding: 5px 12px; background: #FEE2E2; border: 1px solid #FECACA; color: #DC2626; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;">🗑️ Delete Selected (<span id="selectedCount">0</span>)</button>
